112
00:05:23,140 --> 00:05:23,780
Sure.

113
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:26,660
Over here.

114
00:05:26,820 --> 00:05:28,340
One, two, three.

115
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:31,220
Here. Take a look at the photo.

116
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:31,940
Thank you.

117
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:32,860
