385
00:22:52,980 --> 00:22:54,700
She lost her memory after the kiss.

386
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,260
That doesn't make sense, right?

387
00:23:04,700 --> 00:23:05,740
I do look good.

388
00:23:07,980 --> 00:23:09,060
You look great.

389
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:11,500
Seems like you're feeling fine.

390
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:12,100
Xizhou.

391
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:13,740
Take a good rest.

392
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:15,780
We'll leave once the chopper arrives.

393
00:23:16,980 --> 00:23:17,980
Are we leaving so soon?

394
00:23:18,580 --> 00:23:19,860
You've been here long enough.

395
00:23:20,260 --> 00:23:20,740
What's the matter?

396
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,020
Are you reluctant to leave?

397
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:24,700
That's not true.

398
00:23:27,100 --> 00:23:28,260
But

399
00:23:29,460 --> 00:23:31,540
Professor Hans

400
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,780
