401
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:35,700
There isn't enough manpower
in the village,

402
00:23:36,060 --> 00:23:37,700
so I think I should stay and help out.

403
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:48,420
I think that's not the only reason

404
00:23:49,380 --> 00:23:50,500
you want to stay here, right?

405
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:54,780
Xizhou.

406
00:23:55,180 --> 00:23:56,060
I realized

407
00:23:56,340 --> 00:23:58,220
that since you started hanging out
with Gu Ruanruan frequently,

408
00:23:58,300 --> 00:23:59,660
