409
00:24:00,060 --> 00:24:01,300
Has she influenced you?

410
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:04,740
It's been so long since you left.

411
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:06,460
The R&D Department is missing its leader.

412
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:07,820
It's time for you to go back.

413
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:12,460
I understand.

414
00:24:13,540 --> 00:24:15,540
But I still have some business
to take care of.

415
00:24:16,380 --> 00:24:17,780
