in front of all the directors.

422
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:36,140
I don't want that, Xizhou.

423
00:24:36,340 --> 00:24:38,580
You know I hate
business negotiations the most.

424
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:40,700
I don't care
what the board of directors thinks of me.

425
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:42,340
They can say whatever they want.

426
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:44,060
I will count on you

427
00:24:44,540 --> 00:24:45,340
to acquire the herb harvesting rights.

428
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,460
Why are you always like this?

429
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:52,300
I'm feeling dizzy and headache again.

430
00:24:52,940 --> 00:24:54,300
