to the environment here yet,

431
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:55,740
so I can't take too much stress.

432
00:24:59,300 --> 00:25:00,100
Are you having a headache?

433
00:25:01,980 --> 00:25:03,100
You're not acclimated
to the environment, huh?

434
00:25:04,300 --> 00:25:05,700
Say it again.

435
00:25:06,260 --> 00:25:07,100
Does your butt hurt?

436
