It doesn't.

437
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:10,820
Xizhou.

438
00:25:11,260 --> 00:25:12,060
Please...

439
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:16,820
All right.

440
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:20,420
I'll talk to the Chief in the afternoon.

441
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:21,660
Xizhou, you're the best.

442
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:27,300
By the way,

443
00:25:28,620 --> 00:25:30,300
