446
00:25:34,100 --> 00:25:34,900
Don't worry, Xizhou.

447
00:25:35,180 --> 00:25:35,900
Okay.

448
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:38,860
Mind your steps.

449
00:25:50,380 --> 00:25:50,940
Xizhou.

450
00:26:13,620 --> 00:26:15,620
Don't shove.

451
00:26:15,660 --> 00:26:16,940
