need to eat something.

459
00:27:00,740 --> 00:27:02,060
Why are all of you eating here?

460
00:27:09,140 --> 00:27:10,460
This isn't working.

461
00:27:10,940 --> 00:27:12,580
We can't start our work at all.

462
00:27:13,020 --> 00:27:14,500
This place lacks medical care
all year round.

463
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:16,500
Once the villagers heard
that we were giving free consultations,

464
00:27:16,980 --> 00:27:18,780
