00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:16,980
I'm glad to hear that you're all right.

488
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:20,900
Zhizhi, you're here.

489
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:22,580
I was talking to Yunshen about you.

490
00:28:23,100 --> 00:28:23,780
Yunshen.

491
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:25,020
You should talk to Zhizhi...

492
00:28:27,020 --> 00:28:27,500
Hey.

493
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:33,020
The phone call got cut off
all of a sudden.

494
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:33,940
It's fine.

495
00:28:34,100 --> 00:28:35,340
Perhaps the signal was poor.

496
00:28:36,260 --> 00:28:36,940
Madam Jiang.

497
00:28:37,340 --> 00:28:39,020
How are you feeling today?

498
00:28:39,740 --> 00:28:40,460
I'm feeling much better now.

499
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:41,780
I'm fine.

500
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:43,420
Zhizhi.

501
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:45,420
