of me in the past few days.

502
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:47,620
Yunshen told me

503
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:49,140
to thank you on his behalf.

504
00:28:50,580 --> 00:28:51,100
Zhizhi.

505
00:28:51,300 --> 00:28:52,460
You're a nice girl,

506
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:54,260
but you're not proactive enough.

507
00:28:55,180 --> 00:28:57,380
It's all right for girls
to take the initiative.

508
00:28:57,500 --> 00:28:58,980
Look at Ruanruan.

509
00:29:00,700 --> 00:29:01,580
I see, Madam Jiang.

510
00:29:01,820 --> 00:29:03,260
You've recovered.

511
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:04,700
You can be discharged this afternoon.

512
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:07,740
I'll get back to work.

513
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:09,460
- Take a good rest.
- Sure.

514
00:29:18,820 --> 00:29:19,300
Hello.

515
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:21,500
Wait a minute.

516
00:29:25,860 --> 00:29:26,740
Hey, Li Zhen.

517
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:28,580
