522
00:29:34,740 --> 00:29:36,180
Please pay extra attention to his legs.

523
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:37,300
Don't let the wound get infected.

524
00:29:37,940 --> 00:29:39,220
I got it.

525
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:40,820
Thank you so much.

526
00:29:46,380 --> 00:29:47,580
