to the food here, right?

527
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:48,260
Eat this.

528
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:49,220
It can boost your energy.

529
00:29:50,820 --> 00:29:51,500
Thank you,

530
00:29:51,580 --> 00:29:53,260
but I don't have a sweet tooth.

531
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:09,420
We've finally distributed
all the queue numbers.

532
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:11,100
Hopefully, they will follow the schedule

533
00:30:11,140 --> 00:30:12,060
and get their treatments in order.

534
00:30:13,820 --> 00:30:14,620
Don't worry.

535
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:16,260
Chen Le and I will be there tomorrow.

536
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:17,020
Be careful.

537
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:19,620
- Don't worry. Keep walking.
- There's a step here.

538
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:25,820
You're doing pretty well.

539
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:50,300
Be careful.

540
00:30:50,380 --> 00:30:51,100
You should be careful, too.

541
00:30:57,500 --> 00:30:58,180
Are you all right?

542
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:00,420
I'm fine.

543
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:01,740
Zhu Jiu.

544
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:04,660
I have an academic question for you.

545
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:06,300
What is it?

546
00:31:06,620 --> 00:31:09,140
Can low blood sugar make one
lose the memory?

547
00:31:09,380 --> 00:31:10,620
Are you done yet? Let's go.

548
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:14,300
I can't cross this.

549
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:15,220
You should go first.

550
00:31:15,420 --> 00:31:17,380
What makes you think
that I can cross this?

551
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:22,140
Hurry up.

552
00:31:25,540 --> 00:31:26,020
Here.

553
00:31:31,300 --> 00:31:31,820
Are you all right?

554
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:34,740
