557
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:43,860
Are you feeling shy?

558
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:46,020
Fu Yunshen.

559
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:48,780
Since we are having
an academic discussion,

560
00:31:49,100 --> 00:31:51,140
can I ask you a question, too?

561
00:31:51,300 --> 00:31:51,780
Sure.

562
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:54,420
Who is Zhou Zhizhi?

563
00:31:59,220 --> 00:31:59,700
Watch out.

564
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:04,780
Think twice before you give me an answer.

565
00:32:04,860 --> 00:32:05,740
We're not in a hurry.

566
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:13,060
Gu Ruanruan, it's you again.

567
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:15,180
I'm coming. Wait for me.

568
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:16,980
Hello, Mr. Fu.

569
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:19,340
Mr. Xie admires a popular artist a lot.

570
00:32:19,700 --> 00:32:20,820
Her name is Ji Fenghe.

571
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:24,220
But she rarely sells her works publicly.

572
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:26,220
He failed to purchase any of her works
despite having hired many buyers.

573
00:32:27,580 --> 00:32:28,540
Figure out a way.

574
00:32:29,340 --> 00:32:30,460
I tried making offers to her,

575
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:32,060
but she turned down all of them.

576
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:33,660
But coincidentally,

577
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:35,740
she collaborated with your gallery before.

578
00:32:35,860 --> 00:32:37,740
Ms. Gu was in charge of her exhibition.

579
00:32:38,580 --> 00:32:39,780
You may talk to Ms. Gu

580
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:41,380
and see if she can help.

581
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:42,380
Ruanruan?

582
00:32:43,860 --> 00:32:44,420
Yes.

583
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:47,180
Okay. I got it.

584
00:32:56,820 --> 00:32:58,980
What's your relationship with Zhu Jiu?

585
00:32:59,380 --> 00:33:00,060
How did you know each other?

586
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:01,020
When did you become friends?

587
00:33:01,100 --> 00:33:02,580
What stage is your relationship at?

588
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:05,140
Fu Yunshen, please cooperate.

589
00:33:07,060 --> 00:33:07,820
Gu Ruanruan.

590
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:10,380
Go to Xizhou.

591
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:14,140
Fu Yunshen, open the door!

592
00:33:14,580 --> 00:33:15,660
Come out now!

593
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,460
Fu Yunshen!

594
00:33:18,580 --> 00:33:19,380
Ruanruan.

595
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:24,460
Xizhou.

596
00:33:25,820 --> 00:33:26,940
- What brings you here?
- Slowly.

597
00:33:27,420 --> 00:33:28,820
Why are you torturing Yunshen again?

598
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:30,740
Zhizhi asked me to keep an eye on him.

599
00:33:30,860 --> 00:33:32,020
I have to do something about it.

600
00:33:32,940 --> 00:33:34,140
What brings you here?

601
00:33:35,620 --> 00:33:37,300
I want to ask you for a favor.

602
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:39,100
You want me to do you a favor, huh?

603
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:41,260
That's so rare.

604
00:33:41,340 --> 00:33:41,980
Tell me now.

605
00:33:42,140 --> 00:33:43,340
I will do everything for you.

606
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,700
Do you know an artist

607
00:33:46,820 --> 00:33:47,580
named Ji Fenghe?

608
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:48,500
I do.

609
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:49,660
She's my friend.

610
00:33:50,620 --> 00:33:53,380
Do you remember
the seven balls of crumpled paper?

611
00:33:53,620 --> 00:33:54,420
She did that.

612
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:56,420
It left a strong impression on me.

613
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:58,020
Are you looking for her?

614
00:33:58,940 --> 00:34:00,460
I want to purchase one of her artworks.

615
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:01,860
That's easy.

616
00:34:01,980 --> 00:34:02,820
I can help you.

617
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:04,100
Thanks.

618
00:34:04,820 --> 00:34:07,460
It's no biggie.

619
00:34:07,620 --> 00:34:08,740
Anything else I can help you with?

620
00:34:10,820 --> 00:34:11,820
You should rest early.

621
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:12,900
I'll continue my interrogation.

622
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:14,420
Fu Yunshen.

623
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:17,500
Come out now!

624
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:18,820
Now!

625
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,380
- All done.
- You can bring him home.

626
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:48,900
Bye, little boy.

627
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:51,700
All right.

628
00:34:51,780 --> 00:34:54,260
- Thank you.
- Remember to drink more water.

629
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:01,420
Sen.

630
00:35:02,540 --> 00:35:04,020
I have a patient here.

631
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:04,820
He needs your advice.

632
00:35:04,900 --> 00:35:06,060
Dr. Zhu, I want to consult you, too.

633
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:10,540
What is this?

634
00:35:10,780 --> 00:35:12,060
My queue number.

635
00:35:12,550 --> 00:35:15,750
[See you by the drying rack tonight.]

636
00:35:17,140 --> 00:35:18,620
I'll see you tonight.

637
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,340
How childish.

638
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:27,260
What are you talking about?
You look so happy.

639
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:29,100
Let me join your conversation.

640
00:35:29,260 --> 00:35:30,380
You are already a happy person.

641
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:32,020
Gu Ruanruan.

642
00:35:32,700 --> 00:35:34,300
You should be with Xizhou, not here.

643
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:37,060
I'm here to keep an eye on you
on behalf of Zhizhi.

644
00:35:37,140 --> 00:35:38,420
Stop making things up.

645
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:40,340
I always take Zhizhi
as my younger sister.

646
00:35:40,460 --> 00:35:40,940
Besides,

647
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:42,580
stop saying nonsense.

648
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:43,580
Leave now.

649
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:44,860
I'm not leaving.

650
00:35:47,900 --> 00:35:48,540
Professor.

651
00:35:49,260 --> 00:35:51,100
I wish to come over
to take a few photos tomorrow.

652
00:35:51,340 --> 00:35:52,380
Will I disturb you?

653
00:35:52,540 --> 00:35:53,300
Of course not.

654
00:35:53,580 --> 00:35:54,260
You're always welcome here.

655
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:55,580
Thank you.

656
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:56,500
Gu Ruanruan.

657
00:35:56,780 --> 00:35:58,020
You're here with an agenda, huh?

658
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,660
I won't be here
if I don't have an agenda.

659
00:36:17,260 --> 00:36:18,820
You found a very high spot.

660
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:19,620
Be careful.

661
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:23,260
I like your shirt.

662
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:26,340
Dr. Zhu.

663
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:28,180
It seems like you're recovering well.

664
00:36:28,660 --> 00:36:29,620
I'm feeling pretty good.

665
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:30,620
Why did you ask me to come?

666
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:36,700
Nothing special.

667
00:36:36,860 --> 00:36:39,140
I simply want to continue
our academic discussion.

668
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:40,180
Also,

669
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,500
I want to help you restore your memory.

670
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:45,100
I don't talk about work during my break.

671
00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:49,140
Professor, why are you here?

672
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:55,140
So annoying.

673
00:36:55,220 --> 00:36:56,180
Are you able to recall it now?

674
00:36:57,020 --> 00:36:58,740
If you still can't recall it,

675
00:36:58,900 --> 00:37:01,020
I can reenact the scene for you.

676
00:37:01,660 --> 00:37:03,340
It's fine. I can recall what happened.

677
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:04,260
Zhu Jiu.

678
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:06,420
I knew you were faking it.

679
00:37:07,660 --> 00:37:09,540
What? Are you feeling shy again?

680
00:37:10,820 --> 00:37:11,740
Fu Yunshen.

681
00:37:11,900 --> 00:37:14,420
Since this is an academic discussion,

682
00:37:14,620 --> 00:37:16,140
we should both contribute
to the discussion.

683
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:20,020
Do you remember who Zhou Zhizhi is now?

684
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:24,220
You're so curious about me, huh?

685
00:37:24,940 --> 00:37:25,700
Are you jealous?

686
00:37:26,500 --> 00:37:27,700
You're beating around the bush.

687
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:28,700
You must be guilty of something.

688
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:29,900
I have nothing to hide.

689
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:31,180
I can tell you everything.

690
00:37:31,460 --> 00:37:32,060
Really?

691
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:34,500
Make sure you ponder upon it
before you give me the answer.

692
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:36,700
Let's see if the story I heard

693
00:37:36,780 --> 00:37:39,060
is the same
as the one you're going to tell me.

694
00:37:39,220 --> 00:37:41,540
Of course, my version of the story is rue.

695
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:43,820
Gu Ruanruan

696
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:45,580
is always talking nonsense.

697
00:37:45,980 --> 00:37:47,740
My family and the Zhou family
go way back.

698
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:50,860
My mom and the other elders

699
00:37:50,980 --> 00:37:52,980
arranged an engagement for us
when we were babies.

700
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:54,780
However,

701
00:37:54,860 --> 00:37:57,020
I always regard Zhizhi and Ruanruan
as my younger sisters.

702
00:37:58,460 --> 00:38:02,140
So you were childhood sweetheart.

703
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:04,740
Zhu Jiu.

704
00:38:06,300 --> 00:38:08,220
Apparently, Gu Ruanruan
didn't tell you anything.

705
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:15,900
Zhu Jiu.

706
00:38:17,740 --> 00:38:19,260
My brother and I are going back soon.

707
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:23,060
We have stayed here long enough.

708
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:25,100
There are a lot of things in the company
we have to take care of.

709
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:32,980
All right.

710
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:34,780
Then...

711
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:39,860
Is there something in your mind
that you want to tell me?

712
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:54,780
Fu Yunshen.

713
00:38:56,300 --> 00:38:57,060
I...

714
00:39:00,060 --> 00:39:01,700
There's something I want to tell you.

715
00:39:06,980 --> 00:39:08,300
Then,

716
00:39:10,260 --> 00:39:11,420
you can't let this opportunity slip.

717
00:39:12,140 --> 00:39:14,020
I'm leaving very soon.

718
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:21,820
Do you remember

719
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:25,420
that you borrowed 200 dollars from me

720
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:28,900
when we were at the outdoor market?

721
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:30,140
You haven't paid me the interest yet.

722
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:35,340
Double interest, remember?

723
00:39:46,180 --> 00:39:47,020
Keep the change.

724
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,660
Are you done with this now?

725
00:39:53,260 --> 00:39:55,060
Such a money-grubber.

726
00:39:59,660 --> 00:40:00,220
Dr. Zhu.

727
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,390
♪Close your eyes♪

728
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,910
♪Freeze the time♪

729
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,870
♪While I was reading the prologue♪

730
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:16,190
♪The story had already started in secret♪

731
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,550
♪Your smiling face♪

732
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:21,830
♪Appears before me right on time♪

733
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:26,790
♪You're right beside me
when I open my eyes♪

734
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:45,020
Xizhou.

735
00:40:47,780 --> 00:40:48,420
What brings you here?

736
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:49,740
Do you have anything to tell me?

737
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:52,460
Although it's not our first time
seeing each other,

738
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:55,540
I feel different every time I see you.

739
00:40:58,060 --> 00:40:58,740
Cut to the chase.

740
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:02,180
I have got you Ms. Ji's artwork.

741
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:03,260
Tell Chenghuan

742
00:41:03,300 --> 00:41:05,060
to pick it up from her studio tomorrow.

743
00:41:06,460 --> 00:41:07,420
Do we need to pay her anything?

744
00:41:07,780 --> 00:41:08,540
Nothing.

745
00:41:09,380 --> 00:41:10,420
Don't worry.

746
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:11,740
Ms. Ji said

747
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:14,500
that she would offer you
a discounted price for my sake.

748
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:16,860
Thank you, Ruanruan.

749
00:41:17,380 --> 00:41:18,300
Xizhou.

750
00:41:18,500 --> 00:41:20,020
Am I really just getting a thank-you?

751
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:22,020
Are there no other rewards?

752
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:24,740
What do you want?

753
00:41:25,100 --> 00:41:26,060
I want you.

754
00:41:31,020 --> 00:41:32,100
It's getting late.

755
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:33,020
You should go to sleep.

756
00:41:33,980 --> 00:41:34,580
Be good.

757
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:40,380
I'm leaving, then.

758
00:41:41,060 --> 00:41:42,580
I'm going to change
if you continue to stay here.

759
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:47,580
I'm really leaving.

760
00:42:11,460 --> 00:42:12,140
By the way,

761
00:42:12,620 --> 00:42:14,500
how did your negotiation
with the Chief go?

762
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:18,500
He said the herb harvesting rights go
to the local government.

763
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:20,660
That's good.

764
00:42:20,900 --> 00:42:22,580
You should arrange a meeting with them
as soon as possible.

765
00:42:22,700 --> 00:42:23,460
Since we are already here,

766
00:42:23,580 --> 00:42:24,620
let's go back after you close the deal.

767
00:42:25,860 --> 00:42:27,860
Since you're so good
at planning my schedule,

768
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:29,180
you should come with me.

769
00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:30,060
No.

770
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:31,180
The stage is yours.

771
00:42:57,620 --> 00:43:01,220
♪I see you in a dark corner♪

772
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:04,860
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

773
00:43:05,100 --> 00:43:07,180
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

774
00:43:07,420 --> 00:43:11,420
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

775
00:43:12,260 --> 00:43:15,220
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

776
00:43:15,500 --> 00:43:20,660
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

777
00:43:20,820 --> 00:43:26,580
♪That almost fools me♪

778
00:43:36,460 --> 00:43:43,060
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

779
00:43:43,380 --> 00:43:50,020
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

780
00:43:50,300 --> 00:43:56,700
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

781
00:43:56,980 --> 00:44:01,020
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

782
00:44:01,260 --> 00:44:07,140
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

783
00:44:07,460 --> 00:44:13,260
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

784
00:44:22,740 --> 00:44:29,700
♪You feel my pain♪

785
00:44:29,820 --> 00:44:36,780
♪No reason for those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

786
00:44:37,020 --> 00:44:43,700
♪When the meaningless things hit me♪

787
00:44:51,580 --> 00:44:58,060
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

788
00:44:58,740 --> 00:45:05,340
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape
after love sparks fade away♪

789
00:45:05,500 --> 00:45:14,340
♪All I yearn for
is the warmth deep within you♪
